          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="thesis-arrow">▼</div>
        <div class="thesis-layer">
          <div class="thesis-num">3</div>
          <div class="thesis-layer-text">
            <div class="thesis-layer-title">Be sold by AI</div>
            <div class="thesis-layer-sub">Commerce — agentic transactions, AI-native buying, and the agent economy</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

