      <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk'; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center;">🛠️ Free Tools — Try Them Now</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
          
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.08), rgba(6,182,212,0.05)); border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.2); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🎯</div>
            <h4 style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk'; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI Visibility Engine (GEO GPT)</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text); font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Audit how AI sees your brand. Uses Answer Share™ and Prompt Discovery Index™.</p>
